    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "b9a0af46"
      },
      "source": [
        "## 9. ReLU Nonlinearity\n",
        "\n",
        "The **ReLU** (Rectified Linear Unit) clips negative predictions to zero, enforcing the biological constraint that firing rates must be non-negative:\n",
        "\n",
        "$$f_{\\text{ReLU}}(t) = \\max\\bigl(f(t),\\; 0\\bigr)$$\n",
        "\n",
        "where:\n",
        "- $f(t)$ is the raw linear prediction at time $t$ (may be negative)\n",
        "- $f_{\\text{ReLU}}(t)$ is the rectified prediction — guaranteed to be $\\geq 0$\n",
        "\n",
        "After applying ReLU, the scatter plot (Figure 5) shows no points below the $x$-axis, and the Pearson correlation with the PSTH improves because the model no longer outputs physically impossible values.\n"
      ],
      "id": "b9a0af46"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "175e1f8b"
      },
      "source": [
        "### Compute"
      ],
      "id": "175e1f8b"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {
        "colab": {
          "base_uri": "https://localhost:8080/"
        },
        "id": "79f36695",
        "outputId": "3e2f4822-7ba0-41a2-f969-995904d82dae"
      },
      "source": [
        "# Apply ReLU: clip all negative predicted rates to zero\n",
        "f_relu = np.maximum(f_lin, 0)   # shape (T_te,)\n",
        "\n",
        "# Pearson correlation with the test PSTH\n",
        "perf_relu = np.corrcoef(psth_te, f_relu / dt)[0, 1]\n",
        "\n",
        "print(f\"Performance — Linear + ReLU:  r = {perf_relu:.3f}\")\n"
      ],
      "id": "79f36695",
      "outputs": [
        {
          "output_type": "stream",
          "name": "stdout",
          "text": [
            "Performance — Linear + ReLU:  r = 0.611\n"
          ]
        }
      ],
      "execution_count": null
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "239029ba"
      },
      "source": [
        "### Plot"
      ],
      "id": "239029ba"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {
        "colab": {
